Happy People swing ring

Would you like to hang your swing safely on a wooden beam or branch? Then this large sturdy swing ring is a safe tool. This hook has a load capacity up to 200 kg.

Colour: silver
Type: swing ring
Material: steel 
Length: 40 mm
Age: from 4 years old
